Class LazyObjectCreator<A>

  • java.lang.Object

    Contexed
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LazyTypeConverter

    public class LazyObjectCreator<A>
extends AbstractContexed
    This is a lazy evaluated wrapper round the AppContext.makeObject call This allows object construction to be deferred until required. It provides finer control than just caching the results in the AppContext

    If this class is specialised for particular target interfaces then those interfaces can be implemented directly (forwarding onto the inner object).
